        .ui.vertical.stripe.segment.inverted(style='background-image: url("/assets/images/tutorbg.jpg"); background-attachment: fixed; tinted { opacity: 0.8; }')
            .ui.text.container
                h3.ui.header.inverted Flexibility and convenience
                p
                    | One of the best benefits of a tutor is the flexibility of being able fix personalized schedules and timings for classes.
                h4.ui.horizontal.header.divider
                    a According to a Study
                p
                    | Tutoring can also lead to improvements in self-confidence about reading, motivation for reading, and behavior, both among tutees and among peer or cross-age tutors.
        .ui.inverted.vertical.footer.segment
            .ui.container
                .ui.stackable.inverted.divided.equal.height.stackable.grid
                    .five.wide.column
